title: Elk Island Catholic Separate Regional Division No. 41
text:
Elk Island Catholic Separate Regional Division No. 41 or Elk Island Catholic Schools is a <a href="separate%20school">separate school</a> <a href="School%20authority">authority</a> within the Canadian province of <a href="Alberta">Alberta</a> operated out of <a href="Sherwood%20Park">Sherwood Park</a>.
